///    Grid anchors are uniformly spaced over the rectangle \[0, region_width\] ×
///    \[0, region_height\] in sensor-pixel coordinates:
///        anchor(i, j) = ( i · region_width  / (grid_width  - 1),
///                         j · region_height / (grid_height - 1) )
